refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
stringlibvirt_network_get_bridge_name resourcenetwork
Provides a bridge interface name to which a domain may connect a network interface in order to join the network.

&reftitle.parameters;





   network



    Network resource, You can get it using various functions (e.g. libvirt_netwdork_define_xml or libvirt_network_lookup_by_name).
